page.title: 19E.Horsley S. Credits.
page.content:
This area of the 1985 Domesday Project was researched by members of Fetcham Village Women's Institute. We do not live in E.Horsley but it was the nearest available area to Fetcham. Mrs. Mollie Bridge took the photo- graphs and visited the Golf Club; Mrs. Ann Brixey visited the old people's homes; Mrs. Margaret Torr with other members of the Institute's Rambling Group investigated the wood- land and flowers; Mrs. Lesley Hignett researched the farms. Other informa- tion was also supplied by local groups. Mrs. Enid Scriven & Mrs. Barbara Bennett researched the area generally, and with the help of Mrs. Mollie Bridge wrote, edited & finalised the information. We enjoyed ourselves.
